HEADWORD: Non compos mentis
<hw>Non com"pos
men"tis</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. }</mhw> <ety>[L.]</ety> <def>Not of sound
mind; not having the regular use of reason; hence, also, as a noun, an
idiot; a lunatic; one devoid of reason, either by nature or from
accident.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Noncon.</ent>⟦br⟧
